Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.66,Default,Brad,0,0,0,,You're far too inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,青臭い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.62,Default,Brad,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as a true king!
