Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,目に頼りすぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.76,Default,Lin,0,0,0,,You rely on your eye too much!
