Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.60,Default,Brad,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.10,Default,Brad,0,0,0,,I still have this eye, you know!
